Complete in Class  DataCamp Lesson: Introduction to R, Chapter 1: &ldquo;Intro to Basics&rdquo; (by Jonathan Cornelissen). DataCamp Lesson: Reporting with R Markdown, Chapter 1: &ldquo;Authoring R Markdown Reports&rdquo; (by Garrett Grolemund).  
 (Optional) If this was too easy&hellip; 
Learn about (or brush up on) different kinds of objects in R by completing a few other chapters of Introduction to R by Jonathan Cornelissen. Note: these chapters cover base R, not the tidyverse R dialect, but the basic ideas will always be useful.
